250
00:09:19,597 --> 00:09:21,479
because it is so completely disconnected

251
00:09:21,479 --> 00:09:22,219
from the real world.

252
00:09:22,219 --> 00:09:22,920
It's an escape.

253
00:09:23,540 --> 00:09:24,882
But it's not sticky.

254
00:09:24,882 --> 00:09:26,343
I'm not sure I'm going to remember

255
00:09:26,343 --> 00:09:28,866
that I played Candy Crush a lot five or 10 years from now.

