00:09:28,866 --> 00:09:31,188
However, Journey I will remember forever,

257
00:09:31,188 --> 00:09:34,191
because the systems inside of Journey changed me.

258
00:09:34,191 --> 00:09:35,512
And I think about my relationship

259
00:09:35,512 --> 00:09:37,574
to eternal recurrence and the rest of the world

260
00:09:37,574 --> 00:09:39,256
differently now that I've finished playing Journey.

261
00:09:39,256 --> 00:09:41,318
So I think that's an important distinction

262
00:09:41,318 --> 00:09:43,920
to make within games, not in terms of quality,

263
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,822
but in terms of the effect that it's having on the player.

