00:18:36,941 --> 00:18:39,321
place, where you want the narrative to be serving

470
00:18:39,321 --> 00:18:40,482
the performance of the game.

471
00:18:40,482 --> 00:18:42,682
You can't not have that performance and mechanic

472
00:18:42,682 --> 00:18:46,324
present, but you also can't have the story absent either.

